description: Try our easy to follow Teriyaki Beef & Noodles recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Noodle stir-fry,Quick & easy dinner,Low saturated fat,High fibre,High protein,Low sugar,Low fat,Beef
name: Teriyaki Beef & Noodles Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 3 tsp black sesame seeds, toasted (to serve)

recipeInstructions.text: Prepare noodles following packet directions. Combine marinade and vinegar in a bowl. Add the beef strips and toss to combine.
Heat wok over high heat until hot. Swirl 1 teaspoon of oil around wok and add beef, in batches, stir-frying for 2 minutes or until golden. Transfer to a bowl.
Reheat wok. Add remaining oil until hot. Add vegetable mix and stir-fry for 2 minutes. Add kale and 2 tablespoons of water. Cover and cook for 2 minutes or until tender.
Return beef, marinade and noodles to wok. Toss together until well combined and heated through. Serve with sesame seeds sprinkled over.
